"I yam what I yam."<BR>
Popeye</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ulordtowers.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lord Towers</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/9/02 12:54:42 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1627.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Attack Speed Buff... bad news.</span><hr size=1> i can think of one reason why<br>
<br>
speed buff drops weapon speed essentially<br>
<br>
